assetProfile.longBusinessSummary: Fuji P.S Corporation engages in the construction business. The company designs and constructs prestressed concrete structures, including highway and railway bridges, general road bridges, water storage tanks, etc.; repair, reinforcement, and renewal of civil engineering structures, such as precast PC floor slab replacement method, prestress introduction method, electrochemical anticorrosion method, etc.; and prestressed concrete buildings comprising PCaPC construction method, FR and FC plates, PC ring, cast-in-place tension work, etc. It is also involved in the design and construction of seismic reinforcement method for existing buildings; and Manufacture and sale of prestressed concrete product that include JIS bridge girders, sleepers, floor slabs, etc. Fuji P.S Corporation was incorporated in 1954 and is based in Fukuoka City, Japan.
